    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are robust, following a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and lateral stability these cars are known for. Equipped with the factory M-Variable locking differential and individual throttle bodies, this unit offers exceptional throttle response and tactile mechanical feedback. Minor cosmetic patina reflects its status as a well-exercised enthusiast machine, but the powertrain and suspension geometry are perfectly dialed for the next owner.",
